data.description: Live the good life in this corner lot ranch home that offers a balanced blend of rural tranquility and urban convenience. Fall in love with the charming curb appeal that makes it stand out from the rest. Step inside the spacious open floor plan and prepare to be captivated by the sleek interior designs and modern finishes. The kitchen features stainless steel appliances, pendant lighting, a tile backsplash, center island, and a walk-in pantry. This main level offers three generously sized bedrooms, including a primary suite with a walk-in closet and a full ensuite bath. The finished basement offers endless possibilities for recreation and relaxation. This large space is ideal for an owner's retreat or guest suite with barn doors that open to a walk-in closet and a private bath that features a walk-in shower. You could also transform the lower level into a game room, theater, or lounge room with space for a bar. Step outside into your own private paradise. The expansive fenced backyard provides a stunning backdrop for outdoor activities. Whether you're enjoying a quiet morning coffee on the patio or hosting a gathering with friends, the outdoor space is designed to cater to every occasion. Follow the stepping stones to the additional concrete patio that is the perfect spot for a firepit or grill. One block away from the neighborhood park. Situated in the heart of Milliken, you'll find yourself within easy reach of local amenities, entertainment options, and convenient commutes.
